# Eliza Chandler

[Home](../../) > [Estate Phase](../) > [Adventurers](../adventurers) > Female Human Cleric (Life Domain)

**Size &amp; Type**: Medium Humanoid (Human); **Gender**: Female; **Background**: Outlander; **Speed**: 30ft.  
**Class &amp; Levels**: Cleric (Life Domain) 1  
**Proficiency Bonus**: +2; **Armor Class**: 16 (Chainmail); **HP**: 9; **Hit Dice**: 1d8  

Abilities       | STR | DEX | CON | INT | WIS | CHA | SAN
----------------|-----|-----|-----|-----|-----|-----|-----
Raw Score       | 16  | 12  | 13  |  8  | 16  |  8  | 10
Modifier        | +3  | +1  | +1  | -1  | +3  | -1  | +0
Mod+Proficiency | +5  | +3  | +3  | +1  | +5  | +1  | +2
Saving Throws   | +3  | +1  | +1  | -1  | +5* | +1* | +0
Ability Check   | +5* | +1  | +1  | -1  | +5* | -1  | +0

### Proficiencies

* **Saving Throws**: Wisdom &amp; Charisma; **Ability Checks**: Wisdom (Cleric) &amp; Strength (Outlander)
* **Equipment**: All Armor, Shields, Simple Weapons

### Features

* (ACTION) **Attack.** Choose one from below:
  * One-Handed Quarterstaff (Melee Weapon Attack; +5 to hit; reach 5ft; one target; Hit: 1d6+3 bludgeoning damage)
  * Two-Handed Quarterstaff (Melee Weapon Attack; +5 to hit; reach 5ft; one target; Hit: 1d8+3 bludgeoning damage)
  * One-Handed Dagger (Melee Weapon Attack; +5 to hit; reach 5ft; one target; Hit: 1d4+3 piercing damage)
  * One-Handed Dagger (Ranged Weapon Attack; +5 to hit; range 20/60ft; one target; Hit: 1d4+3 piercing damage)
* (BONUS ACTION) **Two Weapon Fighting.** Choose one from below:
  * One-Handed Quarterstaff (Melee Weapon Attack; +5 to hit; reach 5ft; one target; Hit: 1d6 bludgeoning damage)
  * Two-Handed Quarterstaff (Melee Weapon Attack; +5 to hit; reach 5ft; one target; Hit: 1d4+3 bludgeoning damage)
  * One-Handed Dagger (Melee Weapon Attack; +5 to hit; reach 5ft; one target; Hit: 1d4 piercing damage)
  * One-Handed Dagger (Ranged Weapon Attack; +5 to hit; range 20/60ft; one target; Hit: 1d4 piercing damage)
* (PASSIVE) **Divine Domain: Life.** You have access to an expanded spell list and features exclusive to the Life Domain.
* (PASSIVE) **Spellcasting.** See Spellcasting details below.
* (PASSIVE) **Bonus Proficiency.** Gain proficiency with Heavy Armor.
* (PASSIVE) **Disciple of Life.** Whenever you use a spell of 1st level or higher to restore hit points to a creature, the creature regains additional hit points equal to 2 + the spell's level. 

### Spellcasting

* **Spell Slots**: 2/0/0/0/0/0/0/0/0 (Regain all on Long Rest)
* **Spell Save DC**: 13, **Spell Attack Modifier**: +5 
* **Cantrips** (does not expend spell slots)
  * (ACTION) **Sacred Flame.** The target must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or take 1d8 radiant damage. The target gains no benefit from cover for this saving throw. (One Target w/in Sight; Casting Time: 1 Action; Range: 60ft.; Components: V,S; Duration: Instant)
  * (ACTION) **Light.** You touch one object that is no larger than 10 feet in any dimension. Until the spell ends, the object sheds bright light in a 20-foot radius and dim light for an additional 20 feet. (One Target; Casting Time: 1 Action; Range: Touch; Components: V,M; Duration: 1 hour)
  * (ACTION) **Guidance.** You touch one willing creature. Once before the spell ends, the target can roll a 1d4 and add the number rolled to one ability check of its choice. It can roll the die before or after making the ability check. The spell then ends. (One Target; Casting Time: 1 Action; Range: Touch; Components: V,S; Duration: Concentration, up to 1 minute)
* **1st Level Spells** (This character may prepare any 1st Level Cleric Spell)
  * (ACTION) **Bless.** (Always Prepared) You bless up to three creatures of your choice within range. Whenever a target makes an attack roll or a saving throw before the spell ends, the target can roll a 1d4 and add the number rolled to the attack roll or saving throw. (Up to Three Targets; Casting Time: 1 Action; Range: 30ft.; Components: V,S,M; Duration: Concentration, up to 1 minute)
  * (ACTION) **Cure Wounds.** (Always Prepared) A creature you touch regains a number of hit points equal to 1d8 + your spellcasting ability modifier. (One Target; Casting Time: 1 Action; Range: Touch; Components: V,S; Duration: Instant)
  * (ACTION) **Bane.** Up to three creatures of your choice that you can see within range must make Charisma saving throws. Whenever a target that fails this saving throw makes an attack roll or a saving throw before the spell ends, the target must roll a 1d4 and subtract the number rolled from the attack roll or saving throw. (Up to Three Targets; Casting Time: 1 Action; Range: 30ft.; Components: V,S,M; Duration: Concentration, up to 1 minute)
  * (ACTION) **Inflict Wounds.** Make a melee spell attack against a creature you can reach. On a hit, the target takes 3d10 necrotic damage. (One Target; Casting Time: 1 Action; Range: Touch; Components: V,S; Duration: Instant)
  * (ACTION) **Healing Word.** A creature of your choice that you can see within range regains hit points equal to 1d4 + your spellcasting ability modifier. (One Target; Casting Time: 1 Action; Range: 60ft.; Components: V; Duration: Instant)
  * (ACTION) **Detect Magic.** For the duration, you sense the presence of magic within 30 feet of you. If you sense magic in this way, you can use your action to see a faint aura around any visible creature or object in the area that bears magic, and you learn its school of magic if any. (Area; Casting Time: 1 Action; Range: Self; Components: V,S; Duration: Concentration, up to 10 minutes)

### Feats

* (PASSIVE) **Polearm Master**
  * When you take the Attack action and attack with only a glaive, halberd, or quarterstaff, you can use a bonus action to make a melee attack with the opposite end of the weapon. The weapon's damage die for this attack is a d4, and the attack deals bludgeoning damage.
  * While you are wielding a glaive, halberd, pike, or quarterstaff, other creatures provoke an opportunity attack from you when they enter your reach.

### Equipment

* Quarterstaff (Versatile), Dagger (Finesse, Light, Thrown)
* Chainmail (Counts as a Holy Symbol of the Silver Flame, Aspect of Life)
* Priest's Pack (a backpack, a blanket, 10 candles, a tinderbox, an alms box, 2 blocks of incense, a censer, vestments, 2 days of rations, and a waterskin)

